n2t chapter 2

[1] -a = ~a + 1
-a = 2^n-a                      [def]
   = ((2^n-1)-a)+1
   = ~a + 1                     [intuition]

[2] -(-a) = a
2^n-(2^n-a) = 2^n-2^n+a = a

[3] -a = ~(a-1)
-(-a) = a                       [2]
~-a+1 = a                       [1]
~-a   = a-1
-a    = ~(a-1)

[4] x-y = ~(~x+y)
x-y = -(y-x)
    = -(y + (~x + 1))           [1]
    = ~((y + (~x + 1)) - 1)     [3]
    = ~(y + ~x)